data.description: PREMIUM Golf Course Lot with Gorgeous View of 1st Green and 2nd Tee Box on Well Maintained Monarch Golf Course in desirable 55+ Community of ROYAL HIGHLANDS. Beautifully landscaped 3 Bdrm. 2 Bath with hugh under AC Florida Room with wonderful natural light and access to screened lanai. Bedroom has built in Desk/workstation with cabinets to ceiling and can easily be extra guest room. Large Master Bedroom with access to private sitting screen/vinyl room with his & her walk in closets. Lg. Guest bedroom & bath has pocket door for private suite. New vinyl flooring thru out main area,kitchen and guest bath. Inside Laundry room. New Roof 2015, Garage door opener 2020, whirlpool stove & microwave 2023, New sinks & faucets in baths & kitchen, New disposal 2023. Desirable 55+ community of Royal Highlands HOA $212 includes Cable/Internet, Gated/Guard entrance, Golf Course, Great Hall, Rec. Center, Indoor & Outdoor Pools, Softball field, Tennis, shuffle board and pickleball courts. Too many activities to mention. PARTIAL FURNISHED WITH 3 YR. OLD FURNITURE
